```
wismo-tracker/
├── app/
│   ├── page.jsx              ← Main form UI
│   ├── layout.jsx            ← App layout
│   ├── globals.css           ← Global styles
│   └── api/analyze/
│       └── route.js          ← Claude API endpoint
└── components/
    └── ResultCard.jsx        ← Output display
```
---
💡 How It Works
User inputs a customer message + order details
The app sends the data to a Next.js API route
The API route calls Claude with a structured prompt
Claude returns a JSON response with all outputs
The UI renders the results with copy buttons
